description: Redevelopment to provide a 37 storey building (maximum building height 127m AOD) and 4 storey pavilion building (maximum building height 22.47m AOD), comprising 284 residential units, 809 sq.m flexible ground floor retail / financial and professional services / restaurant uses (Use Classes A1-A3) and 413 sq.m commercial (Use Class B1) use, basement car parking, cycle parking, vehicular access from Brook Drive, servicing and plant areas, landscaping and public realm improvements and associated works
